{"title":"AGE动漫客户端的实现","uid":"547cc3060f924df792d2350eb620080c","slug":"acg","date":"2023-01-01T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2023-01-27T12:01:19.524Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/acg.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/sakana/cover.jpg","content":"<h1 id=\"前言\"><a href=\"#前言\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"前言\"></a>前言</h1><p>前阵子看番的时候突发奇想，想着要不自己做一个看番软件。正好刚放假有时间，便开始了这几天的爆肝之旅。</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>项目使用<code>Vue</code>（前端）+<code>Flask</code>（后端）+<code>requests</code>（爬虫）实现，完全零成本地部署在<code>Vercel</code>上。具体的使用见下文。</p></blockquote>\n<p>废话不多说，先看看效果吧。</p>\n<iframe src='https://video.fullcomb.top?url=https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/video/sakana-acg/sakana.m3u8' width=\"100%\" frameborder=\"0\" border=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" mozallowfullscreen=\"mozallowfullscreen\" msallowfullscreen=\"msallowfullscreen\" oallowfullscreen=\"oallowfullscreen\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"webkitallowfullscreen\" security=\"restricted\" sandbox=\"allow-same-origin allow-forms allow-scripts\" style='aspect-ratio: 1.8;'></iframe>\n\n\n<p>除了Windows客户端，我也部署到<code>vercel</code>上，可以直接访问：<a href=\"https://sakana.fullcomb.top/\">Sakana~</a>。</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>这篇文章主要分享我实现这个软件的思路和遇到的坑。中间用到了一些我自认为比较有趣的技术，读者不妨看下去。</p></blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"实现思路\"><a href=\"#实现思路\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"实现思路\"></a>实现思路</h1><h2 id=\"抓包\"><a href=\"#抓包\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"抓包\"></a>抓包</h2><p>首先动漫源肯定不可能我自己整，所以尝试去比较常用的动漫网站上抓包，看看能不能找到有用的<code>API</code>。这里选择AGE动漫。</p>\n<p>在动漫列表这里发现了这个数据包，发现它返回HTML格式的数据，而且是允许跨域的。参数在<code>url</code>中以查询字符串的形式给出，是比较方便的：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/sakana/image-20230101214431450.png\" alt=\"image-20230101214431450\"></p>\n<p>返回的结果也是比较好用的。使用<code>axios</code>获取HTML后，再用<code>cherrio</code>解析即可提取出需要的数据。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/sakana/image-20230101214611243.png\" alt=\"image-20230101214611243\"></p>\n<p>然后是动漫详情页。在这个页面并没有找到显式可用的数据包，但是找到了这个js，里面包含了播放列表，并且给出了视频具体的<code>m3u8</code>链接——这正是我们需要的！</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/sakana/image-20230101220734060.png\" alt=\"image-20230101220734060\"></p>\n<p>查看<code>initiator</code>，可以发现请求来自于这个页面的HTML。所以它应该是以<code>&lt;script&gt;</code>的形式引入的。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/sakana/image-20230101215806197.png\" alt=\"image-20230101215806197\"></p>\n<p>果不其然。所以接下来就很简单了，首先获取到这个HTML，然后使用<code>xpath</code>解析到这个<code>&lt;script&gt;</code>标签的<code>src</code>属性即可。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/sakana/image-20230101220000620.png\" alt=\"image-20230101220000620\"></p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>但是还有一个问题：要获取HTML，但是响应中并没有设置<code>Access-Control-Allow-Origin:&#39;*&#39;</code>，所以会有跨域问题。这点我一开始没想到，后面出现跨域的时候才反应过来。最后是用后端代理解决的，这个后面说。</p></blockquote>\n<p>接下来是播放界面。分析视频的格式：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/sakana/image-20230101220734060.png\" alt=\"image-20230101220734060\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/sakana/image-20230101221435544.png\" alt=\"image-20230101221435544\"></p>\n<p>可以看到视频的格式也是有点乱的。有的是m3u8，有的是以http开头的不明格式，有的甚至就是一串看不懂的东西……但是它们在AGE上都是能播放的。解决办法就是使用正则表达式区别出不同类型的URL，然后使用不同的播放器进行播放。</p>\n<p>最后是搜索页面，很轻松地发现了数据包，但是设置了严格的防跨域：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/sakana/image-20230101222056544.png\" alt=\"image-20230101222056544\"></p>\n<p>解决办法是使用代理：后端先获取这个数据报，然后再以允许跨域的形式转发给前端。思路见下。</p>\n<h2 id=\"代理的实现\"><a href=\"#代理的实现\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"代理的实现\"></a>代理的实现</h2><ol>\n<li><p>因为浏览器的同源策略，直接在<code>javascript</code>中使用<code>axios</code>获取没有设置<code>Access-Control-Allow-Origin:&#39;*&#39;</code>的数据会出现跨域问题。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>而<code>python</code>使用<code>requests</code>可以突破浏览器的限制，直接获取数据。</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>正好前几天做友链留言板阅读<code>Vercel</code>文档的时候，发现<code>Vercel</code>也是可以部署<code>Python</code>项目的，于是便开始尝试。</p>\n<h3 id=\"Vercel部署Flask后端\"><a href=\"#Vercel部署Flask后端\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Vercel部署Flask后端\"></a>Vercel部署Flask后端</h3><p>一番求解，最后在这个仓库找到答案：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/caibingcheng/vercel-flask\">caibingcheng&#x2F;vercel-flask: a vercel flask template (github.com)</a></p>\n<p>直接点击<code>Deploy</code>即可，<code>Vercel</code>会直接创建个人仓库并部署。</p>\n<p>之后只要<code>clone</code>这个仓库，每次提交到<code>github</code>的时候<code>Vercel</code>就会自动部署。</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>使用<code>vercel cil</code>应该也是可以的，但是要写<code>vercel.json</code>，稍微麻烦一些。</p></blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"实现代理\"><a href=\"#实现代理\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"实现代理\"></a>实现代理</h3><p>基本的思路就是将url以查询参数的形式传递给<code>Flask</code>后端，后端使用<code>requests</code>请求url获取响应，然后获取响应的数据，最后加上<code>Access-Control-Allow-Origin:&#39;*&#39;</code>响应头返回。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\"># type参数表示要代理的类型: 1为字符串，2为json，3为图片\n@app.route(&#39;&#x2F;proxy&#39;)\ndef proxy():\n    url &#x3D; request.args.get(&#39;url&#39;)\n    ptype &#x3D; request.args.get(&#39;type&#39;)\n    header &#x3D; &#123;\n        &#39;User-Agent&#39;: &#39;Mozilla&#x2F;5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit&#x2F;537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome&#x2F;103.0.0.0 Safari&#x2F;537.36&#39;,\n        # &#39;Referer&#39;: &#39;http:&#x2F;&#x2F;agedm1.com&#x2F;&#39;\n    &#125;\n    res &#x3D; requests.get(url&#x3D;url, headers&#x3D;header)\n    if ptype &#x3D;&#x3D; &#39;3&#39;:\n        return res.content, 200, &#123;&quot;Content-Type&quot;:&quot;image&#x2F;jpeg&quot;, &#39;Access-Control-Allow-Origin&#39;: &quot;*&quot;&#125;\n    res.encoding &#x3D; &#39;utf-8&#39;\n    if ptype &#x3D;&#x3D; &#39;2&#39;:\n        return jsonify(res.text), 200, &#123;&quot;Content-Type&quot;:&quot;application&#x2F;json&quot;, &#39;Access-Control-Allow-Origin&#39;: &quot;*&quot;&#125;\n    return res.text, 200, &#123;&#39;Access-Control-Allow-Origin&#39;: &quot;*&quot;&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>因为需要的响应要加上允许跨域的头部，所以不能将<code>requests</code>获取的响应原封不动地返回，还要分类别获取数据再重新封装。</p></blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"爬虫的实现\"><a href=\"#爬虫的实现\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"爬虫的实现\"></a>爬虫的实现</h2><p>AGE动漫没有番剧详细的信息。这是一个缺点，在项目中可以改进——要是能把动漫页面做得高大上就好了。</p>\n<p>于是我参考了Plex的设计：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/sakana/image-20230101232415717.png\" alt=\"image-20230101232415717\"></p>\n<p>个人认为这个设计看起来很牛逼的要素主要有以下几点：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>背景图片（而且还有磨砂效果）</li>\n<li>演员表</li>\n<li>评分（前面有一个图标）</li>\n</ol>\n<p>动漫详细的信息，可以在<code>bangumi</code>上爬取：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/sakana/image-20230101232903996.png\" alt=\"image-20230101232903996\"></p>\n<p>在<code>bgm</code>的动漫详情页，可以获取到<strong>角色列表</strong>和<strong>评分</strong>，但遗憾的是没有<strong>横板的背景图片</strong>。</p>\n<p>于是考虑常用的搜图引擎，选择必应搜图。必应图片好在<strong>方便进行筛选</strong>：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/sakana/image-20230101233331607.png\" alt=\"image-20230101233331607\"></p>\n<p>综上，爬虫的实现思路：</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>先在bgm上搜索，选择第一个：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/sakana/image-20230101233546703.png\" alt=\"image-20230101233546703\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>进入详情页，获取如下数据：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/sakana/image-20230101232903996.png\" alt=\"image-20230101232903996\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>最后必应图片上搜索，选择第一个搜索结果。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/sakana/image-20230101233331607.png\" alt=\"image-20230101233331607\"></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>爬虫的代码：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">@app.route(&#39;&#x2F;bangumi&#39;)\ndef bangumi():\n    q &#x3D; request.args.get(&#39;q&#39;)\n    if(len(q) &gt;&#x3D; 7): q &#x3D; q[:math.ceil(len(q)&#x2F;&#x2F;2)]\n    if(re.match(&#39;.*?第.&#123;0,2&#125;&#39;, q)):\n        q &#x3D; re.search(&#39;(.*?)第.&#123;0,2&#125;&#39;, q).group(1)\n    header &#x3D; &#123;\n        &#39;User-Agent&#39;: &#39;Mozilla&#x2F;5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit&#x2F;537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome&#x2F;103.0.0.0 Safari&#x2F;537.36&#39;\n    &#125;\n    # 获取剧照\n    base_url &#x3D; &#39;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;cn.bing.com&#39;\n    res &#x3D; requests.get(url&#x3D;base_url+f&#39;&#x2F;images&#x2F;search?q&#x3D;&#123;q&#125;&amp;qft&#x3D;+filterui:imagesize-wallpaper+filterui:aspect-wide&amp;form&#x3D;IRFLTR&amp;first&#x3D;1&amp;tsc&#x3D;ImageHoverTitle&#39;, headers&#x3D;header)\n    \n    res.encoding &#x3D; res.apparent_encoding\n    data &#x3D; res.content.decode(&#39;utf-8&#39;, &#39;ignore&#39;)\n    \n    html &#x3D; etree.HTML(data)\n    \n    conda_list &#x3D; html.xpath(&#39;&#x2F;&#x2F;a[@class&#x3D;&quot;iusc&quot;]&#x2F;@m&#39;)    \n    \n    # return jsonify(conda_list), 200, &#123;&quot;Content-Type&quot;:&quot;application&#x2F;json&quot;, &#39;Access-Control-Allow-Origin&#39;: &quot;*&quot;&#125;\n    \n    cover &#x3D; re.search(&#39;&quot;murl&quot;:&quot;(.*?)&quot;&#39;, conda_list[0]).group(1)\n    if(re.match(&#39;^http.*?tva.*$&#39;, cover)):\n        cover &#x3D; &#39;http:&#x2F;&#x2F;imgs.acg17.com&#x2F;mw1024&#x2F;&#39;+re.search(&#39;^http.*?tva.*?large\\&#x2F;(.*)$&#39;, cover).group(1)\n    \n    cover_1 &#x3D; re.search(&#39;&quot;murl&quot;:&quot;(.*?)&quot;&#39;, conda_list[1]).group(1)\n    if(re.match(&#39;^http.*?tva.*$&#39;, cover_1)):\n        cover_1 &#x3D; &#39;http:&#x2F;&#x2F;imgs.acg17.com&#x2F;mw1024&#x2F;&#39;+re.search(&#39;^http.*?tva.*?large\\&#x2F;(.*)$&#39;, cover_1).group(1)\n    \n    \n    # 截取长度的一般进行搜索\n    base_url &#x3D; &#39;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;bangumi.tv&#39;\n    \n    res &#x3D; requests.get(url&#x3D;base_url+f&#39;&#x2F;subject_search&#x2F;&#123;q&#125;?cat&#x3D;2&#39;, headers&#x3D;header)\n    res.encoding &#x3D; &#39;utf-8&#39;\n    tree &#x3D; etree.HTML(res.text)\n    try: page &#x3D; tree.xpath(&#39;&#x2F;&#x2F;*[@id&#x3D;&quot;browserItemList&quot;]&#x2F;li&#x2F;a&#x2F;@href&#39;)[0]\n    except: return jsonify(&#123;&#39;tags&#39;: None, &#39;score&#39;: None, &#39;characters&#39;: None, &#39;cover&#39;: [cover, cover_1]&#125;), 200, &#123;&quot;Content-Type&quot;:&quot;application&#x2F;json&quot;, &#39;Access-Control-Allow-Origin&#39;: &quot;*&quot;&#125;\n    \n    res &#x3D; requests.get(url&#x3D;base_url+page, headers&#x3D;header)\n    res.encoding &#x3D; &#39;utf-8&#39;\n    tree &#x3D; etree.HTML(res.text)\n    # tags\n    tags &#x3D; tree.xpath(&#39;&#x2F;&#x2F;*[@id&#x3D;&quot;subject_detail&quot;]&#x2F;div[3]&#x2F;div&#x2F;a&#x2F;span&#x2F;text()&#39;)\n    \n    # 评分\n    score &#x3D; tree.xpath(&#39;&#x2F;&#x2F;*[@id&#x3D;&quot;panelInterestWrapper&quot;]&#x2F;div[1]&#x2F;div&#x2F;div[1]&#x2F;div[2]&#x2F;span[1]&#x2F;text()&#39;)[0]\n    \n    # 角色\n    characters &#x3D; []\n    try: chas &#x3D; tree.xpath(&#39;&#x2F;&#x2F;*[@id&#x3D;&quot;browserItemList&quot;]&#x2F;li&#x2F;div&#39;)\n    except: return jsonify(&#123;&#39;tags&#39;: tags, &#39;score&#39;: score, &#39;characters&#39;: None, &#39;cover&#39;: [cover, cover_1]&#125;), 200, &#123;&quot;Content-Type&quot;:&quot;application&#x2F;json&quot;, &#39;Access-Control-Allow-Origin&#39;: &quot;*&quot;&#125;\n    for cha in chas:\n        try: name &#x3D; cha.xpath(&#39;.&#x2F;div&#x2F;span&#x2F;span&#x2F;text()&#39;)[0]\n        except: name &#x3D; cha.xpath(&#39;.&#x2F;strong&#x2F;a&#x2F;@title&#39;)[0]\n        face &#x3D; &#39;https:&#39;+cha.xpath(&#39;.&#x2F;strong&#x2F;a&#x2F;span&#x2F;span&#x2F;@style&#39;)[0][22:-2]\n        try: cv &#x3D; cha.xpath(&#39;.&#x2F;div&#x2F;span&#x2F;a&#x2F;text()&#39;)[0]\n        except: cv &#x3D; None\n        characters.append(&#123;&#39;name&#39;: name, &#39;face&#39;: face, &#39;cv&#39;: cv&#125;)\n    \n    return jsonify(&#123;&#39;tags&#39;: tags, &#39;score&#39;: score, &#39;characters&#39;: characters, &#39;cover&#39;: [cover, cover_1]&#125;), 200, &#123;&quot;Content-Type&quot;:&quot;application&#x2F;json&quot;, &#39;Access-Control-Allow-Origin&#39;: &quot;*&quot;&#125;\n </code></pre>\n\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>因为要考虑<code>bangumi</code>上没搜到结果以及某些信息不存在的情况，需要使用大量的<code>try catch</code>。再加上需要进行三次<code>http</code>请求，耗时较长，所以这个接口的效率会比较低。</p></blockquote>\n<p>有了这些信息，仿照<code>plex</code>做出来的效果还是比较理想的：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/sakana/image-20230101234300050.png\" alt=\"image-20230101234300050\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"坑\"><a href=\"#坑\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"坑\"></a>坑</h1><p>最最最需要注意的就是<strong>跨域问题</strong>。这不仅是一个后端问题，还是一个前端问题。</p>\n<ol>\n<li>后端需要加上允许跨域的响应头</li>\n<li>前端的请求头里面不能设置自定义头部，不然即使后端允许跨域也会被CROS！</li>\n</ol>\n<p>本项目后端跨域通过代理转发来解决，前端跨域则是在编写代码时注意。</p>\n<hr>\n<p>第二个坑如下：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/sakana/image-20230101235716294.png\" alt=\"image-20230101235716294\"></p>\n<p>意思就是出于安全考虑，<strong>https的网站不允许访问http的网站</strong>。但是<code>vercel</code>部署的网站都是<code>https</code>，所以web端有的视频放不了，而windows客户端就不存在这个问题。这个我实在无能为力。</p>\n<hr>\n<p>第三个是前端的问题，如何<strong>保持固定的宽高比</strong>？</p>\n<p>我一开始直接用CSS的新属性<code>aspect-ratio</code>，但是<code>build</code>的时候发现<code>electron</code><strong>并不支持这个属性！</strong>最后换成了比较常规的保持图片宽高比的思路：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>外面设置一个<code>div</code>，并规定它的宽度。</li>\n<li>里面的图片指定<code>width:100%;height:auto;</code></li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<p>第四个坑是<code>Vue</code>和<code>electron</code>的联调问题。</p>\n<ol>\n<li><code>Vue</code>的路由必须采用<code>hash</code>模式，不然进去的时候白屏。</li>\n<li>项目内路由跳转不能使用<code>&lt;a&gt;</code>标签，而应该使用<code>&lt;router-link&gt;</code>！</li>\n<li>访问外部的资源，需要加上<code>http:</code>或<code>https:</code>。<code>//example.com/a.jpg</code>在浏览器是可以正常访问的，但是<code>electron</code>里面不能，因为它前面的协议是<code>app://</code>，会访问到错误的路径。</li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"总结\"><a href=\"#总结\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"总结\"></a>总结</h1><ol>\n<li><p><code>Vercel+Flask+requests</code>可以说是制作第三方软件获取<code>api</code>的一个非常好的解决方案。<code>Vercel</code>可以部署<code>Python</code>的<code>Flask</code>框架，然后又可以在框架中集成爬虫那一套——可谓是适用性极广。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>这个项目我之后想到有意思的点子的话会继续做进去的，这几天拿肾肝。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>electron</code>做出的软件内存开销太大，以后选择技术栈的话最好不要用它。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>前端项目真的是一次编写，到处部署，但是开发客户端最好还是不同平台选择专门的技术。毕竟那样用户体验好一些，开发者累一些又如何呢。</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n","text":"前言前阵子看番的时候突发奇想，想着要不自己做一个看番软件。正好刚放假有时间，便开始了这几天的爆肝之旅。 项目使用Vue（前端）+Flask（后端）+requests（爬虫）实现，完全零成本地部署在Vercel上。具体的使用见下文。 废话不多说，先看看效果吧。 除了Windows客...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"8.2k","symbolsTime":"7 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"兴趣","slug":"兴趣","count":4,"path":"api/categories/兴趣.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Vue","slug":"Vue","count":4,"path":"api/tags/Vue.json"},{"name":"electron","slug":"electron","count":1,"path":"api/tags/electron.json"},{"name":"爬虫","slug":"爬虫","count":1,"path":"api/tags/爬虫.json"},{"name":"Vercel","slug":"Vercel","count":2,"path":"api/tags/Vercel.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%89%8D%E8%A8%80\"><span class=\"toc-text\">前言</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E6%80%9D%E8%B7%AF\"><span class=\"toc-text\">实现思路</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%8A%93%E5%8C%85\"><span class=\"toc-text\">抓包</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BB%A3%E7%90%86%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">代理的实现</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Vercel%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2Flask%E5%90%8E%E7%AB%AF\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Vercel部署Flask后端</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E4%BB%A3%E7%90%86\"><span class=\"toc-text\">实现代理</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%88%AC%E8%99%AB%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">爬虫的实现</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%9D%91\"><span class=\"toc-text\">坑</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93\"><span class=\"toc-text\">总结</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"砂糖","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/build/Ryza/avatar.png","link":"/","description":"盐港鸣笛声  催扬帆出海<br>方觉时光匆匆已过三载<audio controls><source src=\"http://music.163.com/song/media/outer/url?id=1366594775.mp3\"></audio>","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Satoing","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"iconfont icon-bilibili-fill","link":"https://space.bilibili.com/52750318"},"Leetcode":{"icon":"iconfont icon-leetcode","link":"https://leetcode.cn/u/satoing/"}}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"Yealico——LSP专属的信息聚合软件(iOS ver.)","uid":"d15c090de583341effbf1fff21e266e4","slug":"Yealico","date":"2023-01-27T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2023-01-29T07:59:58.744Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Yealico.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/yealico/image-20230127165412861.png","text":"前言这篇文章给大家分享一个iOS上的软件：Yealico。 这是一个信息聚合软件，官方的描述是：“使用Yealico可以将您关心的web内容轻松整理在一处。” RSS的误用之前玩RSS的时候我就在思考信息聚合的方案。RSS的适用面是比较广的，如果网站本身提供了RSS feed的话...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"3k","symbolsTime":"3 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"分享","slug":"分享","count":11,"path":"api/categories/分享.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Yealico","slug":"Yealico","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Yealico.json"}],"author":{"name":"砂糖","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/build/Ryza/avatar.png","link":"/","description":"盐港鸣笛声  催扬帆出海<br>方觉时光匆匆已过三载<audio controls><source src=\"http://music.163.com/song/media/outer/url?id=1366594775.mp3\"></audio>","socials":{"gith